data.description: This meticulously maintained residence, a true gem boasting numerous updates, is move-in ready. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail that has been poured into this home. The brand-new Jacuzzi spa is the perfect oasis for relaxation and rejuvenation, offering the ultimate retreat after a long day. Located on the paved area of the spacious backyard giving a great spot for gatherings and barbecues.  Plus, you'll find two spacious storage sheds to accommodate all your storage needs. One car garage to keep your vehicle safe and clean. The electrical panel has been completely replaced, and all the electrical systems have been brought up to code, ensuring peace of mind for you and your family. The plumbing has been updated, and a new water heater installed. The bathroom has been beautifully redone, featuring a new shower and tub. In addition to the interior upgrades, this home has new top-of-the-line front and back hurricane-grade doors, offering unparalleled security and protection.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this Seminole sanctuary your own. This home is ready for you to move in and start creating lasting memories. Call to schedule a viewing today and find out why it's priced so well!
